title: Kendall Jenner: Takes Money but Flees Photo Shoots?
description:
Kendall Jenner may be the world’s highest paid model, but even she may not understand what she’s obligated to do under her contract with Italian fashion brand, Liu Jo.  Tune in to hear about Kendall’s failure under the agreement and the brand’s ongoing lawsuit!
